669
00:29:56,298 --> 00:29:59,466
[Will] <i>Cool. But Tuesdays are bad
'cause your mom comes over.</i>

670
00:29:59,467 --> 00:30:01,468
[Sylvia chuckles]

671
00:30:01,469 --> 00:30:04,430
[Sylvia] <i>Thank you for capitalizing
her name. Very respectful.</i>

672
00:30:04,431 --> 00:30:07,349
[Will] <i>She's a working dominatrix,
so she demands respect.</i>

673
00:30:07,350 --> 00:30:09,894
[Sylvia] <i>Nice try. My mom only goes
to duck ponds and church.</i>

674
00:30:09,895 --> 00:30:11,312
[Will] <i>That actually sounds nice.</i>

675
00:30:11,313 --> 00:30:12,397
[Sylvia] <i>It is nice.</i>

676
00:30:12,939 --> 00:30:14,274
[Will chuckles]

677
00:30:14,858 --> 00:30:15,901
[Sylvia chuckles]
